{"tid":628032,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"日本「新品種」痴漢","createTime":"2018-04-13T12:46:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-13T14:59:04.000Z","uid":181416,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4454def951024985751a0115c6d05216749594ef","tid":628032,"uid":181416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T12:46:47.000Z","msg":"日本電車痴漢非禮車上女乘客，已令女性人人自危，然而當地近來出現「新品種」痴漢，可能更加難防：他們只聞女性體味，而不會與對方有身體接觸，以逃避法網。<br />\n<br />\n痴漢一面靠近女學生，一面聞她的體味。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/13/204501_7402fde393010a5633c5c3b5ad38c385.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F13%2F204501_7402fde393010a5633c5c3b5ad38c385.png&h=3ba5ddef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當地有節目揭示這些痴漢的犯案手法：他們會先在月台物色對象，然後跟隨目標女性上車，全程不會出手觸碰她，只會靠近去聞她的體味，並偷偷在電車上自慰。<br />\n<br />\n這種痴漢如若被捕，大多只會被當局罰款了事，並不會遭到拘留。<br />\n<br />\n有當地網民拍下一名痴漢的犯罪實錄，並上載上網。從影片可見，該名男子先靠近一位女學生，一面聞她的體味，一面用手搓揉自己下體，非常噁心。<br />\n<br />\n有網民對痴漢所為表示不解，亦有網民認為，只是聞女性的味道已可自慰，算得上是「變態高級者」。<br />\n<br />\n（綜合報道）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/13/204551_f87ffbb6a33bf8ce590a872252d55f6e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F13%2F204551_f87ffbb6a33bf8ce590a872252d55f6e.png&h=750ee1b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知香港咁做犯唔犯法呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08558a130d2de7e04719ee76d275ce4770132979","tid":628032,"uid":16777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T12:49:28.000Z","msg":"淨聞氣味咁又算唔算非禮？"},{"pid":"5331f1d2d587d61222685f97012ffa9e5fce00b9","tid":628032,"uid":179962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T12:51:06.000Z","msg":"變態高級者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8102e868d0c65c127f8201e8996967c60c251c90","tid":628032,"uid":181416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08558a130d2de7e04719ee76d275ce4770132979","tid":628032,"uid":16777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T12:49:28.000Z","msg":"淨聞氣味咁又算唔算非禮？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T12:51:08.000Z","msg":"應該唔算 但聞味都打到飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ee550cbe916fe46dbb9849ae1e0b87acd73e00e","tid":628032,"uid":126977,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T12:51:11.000Z","msg":"係咪就快練成念力打飛機級數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a892aaebdaa56ecb3a45294a5251b1c8db81919f","tid":628032,"uid":181416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5331f1d2d587d61222685f97012ffa9e5fce00b9","tid":628032,"uid":179962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T12:51:06.000Z","msg":"變態高級者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T12:51:54.000Z","msg":"靠味打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30cc357071f0707b77001d9be4649506281c5fe6","tid":628032,"uid":181416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ee550cbe916fe46dbb9849ae1e0b87acd73e00e","tid":628032,"uid":126977,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T12:51:11.000Z","msg":"係咪就快練成念力打飛機級數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTim